description: Est. in the summer of 2008 in lovely SoCal San Diego, Beachin' Boba is the first and only mobile concessionaire in all of San Diego and North County to bring you delicious boba drinks, healthy & refreshing green teas, epically good smoothies, "OMG this is so bomb" fruit slushies, fresh hand-squeezed lemonade, specialty coffees, hella good ice cream, wicked yummy root beer float and killer baked ch-ch-ch-Churros! You will not be able to resist this splendid selection of goodies and MORE, so why try?In addition to serving up some awesomeness to your day, Beachin' Boba also takes pride in the community they live and work in. You can always find them participating in local events that give back to their community whenever possible...school fundraisers, sports tournaments, and many, many, more. If it's a worthy cause, they'll be there.For all your special occasions and events, big and small, give this family-owned and operated truck a call. They are sure to make your day a very beachin' one to remember.
name: Beachin Boba
